item.title: P!nk - What About Us - Key of G
item.description:
This tutorial will show you how to play What About Us on the ukulele by Pink. The chords used are Em C G.
If you found this video useful please subscribe and share with your friends. If you want to be notified of future videos please click on bell next to subscribe.
Video created on the iPad Pro using Luma Fusion. The uke chord font is Chordette for Education, available at ukefarm.com.

item.title: P!nk - Just Like Fire - Key of Em
item.description: Em, C, G, A...syncopated strum on this one. Listen to the recording, check out the strum indicators...see what you can do! The X means you mute (stop) the strings.
